title: Animal Disasters, Part 2: Too Dark for Texas
description:
You know how we did a live show in Austin centered around animal mishaps? Well, there were several stories you submitted that we did not feel comfortable reading into a microphone in front of actual people. So we saved them for this episode, where we could read them into a microphone to digital people, who are not real. Topics include:
- Ocean's 11 But Dogs
- Prissy, the Radical Feminist Cow
- Woodchucks + Fireworks = John Wuck
- Tom Hanks as a unit of measurement
- Unregistered Iowa Petting Zoo(s)
